{"id":50221,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":12,"day":24}],"page":"12","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"世纪风","column":"","genre":"","count":"386","ytitle":"","mtitle":"红叶之献","ftitle":"","authors":["张菽"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"张菽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霜花装点十月的秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗外——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边木叶萧萧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隐约听得一阵歌吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧女的羊铃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇落在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迢遥的萝水间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我悄悄地想起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酡红的木叶下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾有你英勇的风姿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，落叶如墳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苔铺满的径上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只一恁那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西风的挪揄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争斗中，我欣幸认识你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个工厂的细胞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无厌的女孩子；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不缺乏强暴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骄傲地忍耐着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无极的灾祸与苦辛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟随自由的旗帜遇进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还有太多的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜜饯的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天真的友情；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像花一般地顺从时序，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是新的中国的女性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切女性的美点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都聚在你一身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你爱祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你爱自己的民族；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的热成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能征服一队大军!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人世间原只有爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是至上至高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死，也在它的面前拜倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我忘不掉那一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩护大队撤退，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你迎上敌人的枪刺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在酡红的木叶下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意然做了自愿的牺牲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的伟大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超过任何英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年，霜花又装点残秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然黑暗依旧密布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们却已冲出重围。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢地生，勇敢地死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要放喉为你酣唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌颂你贡献年青的生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那木叶酡红的园林。"}]}